2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a cooperation scheme among spatially distributed stations, which is a common theme in networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper analyzes the performance of a communication system, which can be viewed as a control system. 
4. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking) - The paper deals with a communication system and its outage statistical parameters, which is a core topic in communications and networking. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper discusses a cooperation scheme among multiple relays, which can be viewed as a multiagent system.
